description:
Stak is joined by NBA vet Jelani McCoy on a special edition of WHATS BURNIN. The boys breakdown the highly-anticipated returns of Klay Thompson & Kyrie Irving. Plus, they look ahead to the biggest matchups of the week and talk NFL playoffs.
